      <title>南非总统签署土地征用法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/south-african-president-signs-off-on-land-expropriation-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨同意一项新法律，该法律使国家可以更容易地为了公共利益征用土地，但必须支付公平的补偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/south-african-president-signs-off-on-land-expropriation-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 14:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯称已在美国投资 7700 亿美元，MBS 则着眼于更多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/saudi-arabia-says-770-billion-invested-in-us-as-mbs-eyes-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯在美国的投资超过 7700 亿美元，并表示，预计在沙特进行广泛的经济改革的同时，与华盛顿的关系“将继续蓬勃发展”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/saudi-arabia-says-770-billion-invested-in-us-as-mbs-eyes-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:57:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与丹麦争吵之际，丹麦希望增加格陵兰防务支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/denmark-wants-to-spend-more-on-greenland-defense-amid-trump-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦国防部长希望到 2033 年将这个北欧国家的总军费开支提高到 5000 亿克朗（700 亿美元）以上，以加大对北极地区安全的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/denmark-wants-to-spend-more-on-greenland-defense-amid-trump-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:55:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰的马丁再次出任第二任总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ireland-s-martin-returns-as-prime-minister-for-second-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰共和党领袖迈克尔·马丁 (Micheal Martin) 在去年 11 月的选举中当选为总理，主要现任执政联盟伙伴重新执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ireland-s-martin-returns-as-prime-minister-for-second-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冰岛通过众包方式削减政府开支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/iceland-is-crowdsourcing-ways-to-cut-state-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长达迪马尔克里斯托弗森 (Dadi Mar Kristofersson) 表示，冰岛正在向民众征集有关预算节约的想法，以确保纳税人的钱得到合理使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/iceland-is-crowdsourcing-ways-to-cut-state-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:22:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普农业部长人选将因生物燃料问题成为参议院热门话题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-s-agriculture-pick-set-for-senate-hot-seat-over-biofuels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统提名的美国农业监管人曾经是一个团体的负责人，而该团体是美国最受欢迎的农产品——生物燃料的最强烈反对者之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-s-agriculture-pick-set-for-senate-hot-seat-over-biofuels</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度、中国外交官将在北京会晤，寻求改善关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/india-china-diplomats-to-meet-in-beijing-to-pursue-better-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和印度高级外交官将于下周在北京会晤，这两个拥有核武器的邻国正试图修复近五年前因边界争端而受损的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/india-china-diplomats-to-meet-in-beijing-to-pursue-better-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 12:55:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
